_sText:
Updated for the 4HM Gun Game Mod by ivix <http://www.bahamutzero.com>:
(most) weapons, buyzones, bomb sites, and hostages have been removed.

Spawn points: 40

=============================
Original fy_icecabin_gzm.txt:

fy_icecabin_gzm by gozemem

version 1.0 2005-09-29

gozemem@yahoo.co.uk
email bugs to above address

----------------------

A simple variation on fy_iceworld. 
This one contains a cosy cabin 
and shootable ice. 

All weapons are spawned on map start. 

----------------------

Installation: extract the zip to 
your cstrike directory. The zip 
contains the following:

maps
  fy_icecabin_gzm.bsp
  fy_icecabin_gzm.txt


The nav file for robots is contained 
in the BSP.

----------------------
